descriptionHtml:
Xhaustuld is two story player home in whiterun. It's generally finished as it is. Has a Smelter, Anvil, Tanning Rack, Workbench, and Grindstone. One chest inside is not owned, never thought it too important to change ownership. Also renames the town to Calchester, and renames Vilmyr Inn 'Frost Troll Inn' but I didn't change the sign. I was going to do more with it but decided against it.Â 


[b]Edit[/b]:
I didn't remove ANYTHING from the area, I simply moved him over to the mill. If he isn't there wait and he should reappear. I haven't had any of the bugs that have been reported. It's likely your game, not the mod. Additionally, I'm going to change the name back to Ivarstead and rename the inn when I get the time. I only made this because I had nothing better to do it's bound to have problems.
